3299 HandleAuraModIncreaseSpeed(aurApp, mode, apply);
3300}
3301
3302void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModIncreaseFlightSpeed(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
3303{
3304 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_SEND_FOR_CLIENT_MASK))
3305 return;
3306
3307 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
3308 if (mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK)
3309 target->UpdateSpeed(MOVE_FLIGHT, true);
3310
3312 if (GetAuraType() == SPELL_AURA_MOD_INCREASE_MOUNTED_FLIGHT_SPEED)
3313 {
3314 // do not remove unit flag if there are more than this auraEffect of that kind on unit on unit
3315 if (mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_SEND_FOR_CLIENT_MASK && (apply || (!target->HasAuraType(SPELL_AURA_MOD_INCREASE_MOUNTED_FLIGHT_SPEED) && !target->HasAuraType(SPELL_AURA_FLY))))
3316 {
3317 target->SetCanFly(apply);
3318
3319 if (!apply && target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_UNIT && !target->IsLevitating())
3320 target->GetMotionMaster()->MoveFall();
3321 }
3322
3324 if (mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL)
3325 {
3326 //Players on flying mounts must be immune to polymorph
3327 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
3328 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_POLYMORPH, apply);
3329
3330 // Dragonmaw Illusion (overwrite mount model, mounted aura already applied)
3331 if (apply && target->HasAuraEffect(42016, 0) && target->GetMountID())
3332 target->SetUInt32Value(UNIT_FIELD_MOUNTDISPLAYID, 16314);
3333 }
3334 }
3335
3336 if (Player* targetPlayer = target->ToPlayer())
3337 {
3338 sScriptMgr->AnticheatSetUnderACKmount(targetPlayer);
3339 }
3340}

3612 if (aura_immunity_list.empty())
3613 {
3614 // Roots, OK
3615 if (GetMiscValue() & (1 << 0))
3616 {
3617 mechanic_immunity_list = (1 << MECHANIC_SNARE);
3618
3619 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_SNARE, apply);
3620 aura_immunity_list.push_back(SPELL_AURA_MOD_ROOT);
3621 }
3622 // Taunt, OK
3623 if (GetMiscValue() & (1 << 1))
3624 {
3625 aura_immunity_list.push_back(SPELL_AURA_MOD_TAUNT);
3626 }
3627 // Crowd-Control auras?
3628 if (GetMiscValue() & (1 << 2))
3629 {
3630 mechanic_immunity_list = (1 << MECHANIC_POLYMORPH) | (1 << MECHANIC_DISORIENTED);
3631
3632 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_POLYMORPH, apply);
3633 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_DISORIENTED, apply);
3634 aura_immunity_list.push_back(SPELL_AURA_MOD_CONFUSE);
3635 }
3636 // Interrupt, OK
3637 if (GetMiscValue() & (1 << 3))
3638 {
3639 mechanic_immunity_list = (1 << MECHANIC_INTERRUPT);
3640
3641 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_INTERRUPT, apply);
3642 }
3643 // Transform?
3644 if (GetMiscValue() & (1 << 4))
3645 {
3646 aura_immunity_list.push_back(SPELL_AURA_TRANSFORM);
3647 }
3648 // Stun auras breakable by damage (Incapacitate effects), OK
3649 if (GetMiscValue() & (1 << 5))
3650 {
3651 mechanic_immunity_list = (1 << MECHANIC_KNOCKOUT);
3652
3653 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_KNOCKOUT, apply);
3654 }
3655 // // Slowing effects
3656 if (GetMiscValue() & (1 << 6))
3657 {
3658 mechanic_immunity_list = (1 << MECHANIC_SNARE);
3659
3660 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_SNARE, apply);
3661 aura_immunity_list.push_back(SPELL_AURA_MOD_DECREASE_SPEED);
3662 }
3663 // Charm auras?, 90%
3664 if ((GetMiscValue() & (1 << 7)))
3665 {
3666 mechanic_immunity_list = (1 << MECHANIC_CHARM);
3667
3668 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_CHARM, apply);
3669 aura_immunity_list.push_back(SPELL_AURA_MOD_CHARM);
3670 aura_immunity_list.push_back(SPELL_AURA_MOD_POSSESS);
3671 }
3672 // UNK
3673 // if ((GetMiscValue() & (1 << 8)))
3674 // {
3675 // }
3676 // Fear, OK
3677 if (GetMiscValue() & (1 << 9))
3678 {
3679 mechanic_immunity_list = (1 << MECHANIC_FEAR);
3680
3681 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_FEAR, apply);
3682 aura_immunity_list.push_back(SPELL_AURA_MOD_FEAR);
3683 }
3684 // Stuns, OK
3685 if (GetMiscValue() & (1 << 10))
3686 {
3687 mechanic_immunity_list = (1 << MECHANIC_STUN);
3688
3689 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_STUN, apply);
3690 aura_immunity_list.push_back(SPELL_AURA_MOD_STUN);
3691 }
3692 }
3693
3694 // apply immunities
3695 for (std::list <AuraType>::iterator iter = aura_immunity_list.begin(); iter != aura_immunity_list.end(); ++iter)
3696 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_STATE, *iter, apply);
3697
3698 // Patch 3.0.3 Bladestorm now breaks all snares and roots on the warrior when activated.
3699 if (GetId() == 46924)
3700 {
3701 if (apply)
3702 {
3703 target->resetAttackTimer();
3704 target->resetAttackTimer(OFF_ATTACK);
3705 }
3706
3707 // Knockback and hex
3708 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_EFFECT, SPELL_EFFECT_KNOCK_BACK, apply);
3709 }
3710
3711 if (apply && GetSpellInfo()->HasAttribute(SPELL_ATTR1_IMMUNITY_PURGES_EFFECT))
3712 {
3713 target->RemoveAurasWithMechanic(mechanic_immunity_list, AURA_REMOVE_BY_DEFAULT, GetId());
3714 for (std::list <AuraType>::iterator iter = aura_immunity_list.begin(); iter != aura_immunity_list.end(); ++iter)
3715 target->RemoveAurasByType(*iter);
3716 }
3717}
3718
3719void AuraEffect::HandleModMechanicImmunity(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
3720{
3721 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
3722 return;
3723
3724 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
3725 uint32 mechanic = 0;
3726
3727 switch (GetId())
3728 {
3729 case 46924: // BladeStorm
3730 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_STUN, apply);
3731 break;
3732 case 34471: // The Beast Within
3733 case 19574: // Bestial Wrath
3734 mechanic = IMMUNE_TO_MOVEMENT_IMPAIRMENT_AND_LOSS_CONTROL_MASK;
3735 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_CHARM, apply);
3736 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_DISORIENTED, apply);
3737 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_FEAR, apply);
3738 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_ROOT, apply);
3739 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_SLEEP, apply);
3740 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_SNARE, apply);
3741 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_STUN, apply);
3742 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_FREEZE, apply);
3743 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_KNOCKOUT, apply);
3744 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_POLYMORPH, apply);
3745 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_BANISH, apply);
3746 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_SHACKLE, apply);
3747 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_TURN, apply);
3748 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_HORROR, apply);
3749 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_DAZE, apply);
3750 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_SAPPED, apply);
3751 break;
3752 case 42292: // PvP trinket
3753 case 59752: // Every Man for Himself
3754 case 65547: // PvP trinket for Faction Champions (ToC 25)
3755 case 53490: // Bullheaded
3756 case 46227: // Medalion of Immunity
3757 mechanic = IMMUNE_TO_MOVEMENT_IMPAIRMENT_AND_LOSS_CONTROL_MASK;
3758 target->RemoveAurasByType(SPELL_AURA_PREVENTS_FLEEING); // xinef: Patch 2.3.0 PvP Trinkets: Insignia of the Alliance, Insignia of the Horde, Medallion of the Alliance, and Medallion of the Horde now clear the debuff from Judgement of Justice.
3759 // Actually we should apply immunities here, too, but the aura has only 100 ms duration, so there is practically no point
3760 break;
3761 case 54508: // Demonic Empowerment
3762 mechanic = (1 << MECHANIC_SNARE) | (1 << MECHANIC_ROOT);
3763 target->RemoveAurasByType(SPELL_AURA_MOD_STUN);
3764 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_SNARE, apply);
3765 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_ROOT, apply);
3766 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, MECHANIC_STUN, apply);
3767 break;
3768 default:
3769 if (GetMiscValue() < 1)
3770 return;
3771 mechanic = 1 << GetMiscValue();
3772 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, GetMiscValue(), apply);
3773 break;
3774 }
3775
3776 if (apply && GetSpellInfo()->HasAttribute(SPELL_ATTR1_IMMUNITY_PURGES_EFFECT))
3777 {
3778 // Xinef: exception for purely snare mechanic (eg. hands of freedom)!
3779 if (mechanic == (1 << MECHANIC_SNARE))
3780 target->RemoveMovementImpairingAuras(false);
3781 else
3782 target->RemoveAurasWithMechanic(mechanic, AURA_REMOVE_BY_DEFAULT, GetId());
3783 }
3784}
3785
3786void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModEffectImmunity(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
3787{
3788 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
3789 return;
3790
3791 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
3792
3793 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_EFFECT, GetMiscValue(), apply);
3794
3795 // when removing flag aura, handle flag drop
3796 Player* player = target->ToPlayer();
3797 if (!apply && player && (GetSpellInfo()->AuraInterruptFlags & AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_IMMUNE_OR_LOST_SELECTION))
3798 {
3799 if (player->InBattleground())
3800 {
3801 if (Battleground* bg = player->GetBattleground())
3802 bg->EventPlayerDroppedFlag(player);
3803 }
3804 else
3805 sOutdoorPvPMgr->HandleDropFlag(player, GetSpellInfo()->Id);
3806 }
3807}

3821
3822void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModSchoolImmunity(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
3823{
3824 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
3825 return;
3826
3827 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
3828
3829 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_SCHOOL, GetMiscValue(), (apply));
3830
3831 if (GetSpellInfo()->Mechanic == MECHANIC_BANISH)
3832 {
3833 if (apply)
3834 target->AddUnitState(UNIT_STATE_ISOLATED);
3835 else
3836 {
3837 bool banishFound = false;
3838 Unit::AuraEffectList const& banishAuras = target->GetAuraEffectsByType(GetAuraType());
3839 for (Unit::AuraEffectList::const_iterator i = banishAuras.begin(); i != banishAuras.end(); ++i)
3840 if ((*i)->GetSpellInfo()->Mechanic == MECHANIC_BANISH)
3841 {
3842 banishFound = true;
3843 break;
3844 }
3845 if (!banishFound)
3846 target->ClearUnitState(UNIT_STATE_ISOLATED);
3847 }
3848 }
3849
3850 if (apply && GetMiscValue() == SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL)
3851 target->RemoveAurasWithInterruptFlags(AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_IMMUNE_OR_LOST_SELECTION);
3852
3853 // remove all flag auras (they are positive, but they must be removed when you are immune)
3854 if (GetSpellInfo()->HasAttribute(SPELL_ATTR1_IMMUNITY_PURGES_EFFECT)
3855 && GetSpellInfo()->HasAttribute(SPELL_ATTR2_FAIL_ON_ALL_TARGETS_IMMUNE))
3856 target->RemoveAurasWithInterruptFlags(AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_IMMUNE_OR_LOST_SELECTION);
3857
3858 // TODO: optimalize this cycle - use RemoveAurasWithInterruptFlags call or something else
3859 if ((apply)
3860 && GetSpellInfo()->HasAttribute(SPELL_ATTR1_IMMUNITY_PURGES_EFFECT)
3861 && GetSpellInfo()->IsPositive()) //Only positive immunity removes auras
3862 {
3863 uint32 school_mask = GetMiscValue();
3864 Unit::AuraApplicationMap& Auras = target->GetAppliedAuras();
3865 for (Unit::AuraApplicationMap::iterator iter = Auras.begin(); iter != Auras.end();)
3866 {
3867 SpellInfo const* spell = iter->second->GetBase()->GetSpellInfo();
3868 if ((spell->GetSchoolMask() & school_mask)//Check for school mask
3869 && GetSpellInfo()->CanDispelAura(spell)
3870 && !iter->second->IsPositive() //Don't remove positive spells
3871 && spell->Id != GetId()) //Don't remove self
3872 {
3873 target->RemoveAura(iter);
3874 }
3875 else
3876 ++iter;
3877 }
3878 }
3879}

3907/********************************/
3908
3909void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModResistanceExclusive(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
3910{
3911 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
3912 return;
3913
3914 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
3915
3916 for (int8 x = SPELL_SCHOOL_NORMAL; x < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; x++)
3917 {
3918 if (GetMiscValue() & int32(1 << x))
3919 {
3920 int32 amount = target->GetMaxPositiveAuraModifierByMiscMask(SPELL_AURA_MOD_RESISTANCE_EXCLUSIVE, 1 << x, this);
3921 if (amount < GetAmount())
3922 {
3923 float value = float(GetAmount() - amount);
3924 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_RESISTANCE_START + x), BASE_VALUE, value, apply);
3925 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
3926 target->ApplyResistanceBuffModsMod(SpellSchools(x), aurApp->IsPositive(), value, apply);
3927 }
3928 }
3929 }
3930}
3931
3932void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModResistance(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
3933{
3934 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
3935 return;
3936
3937 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
3938
3939 for (int8 x = SPELL_SCHOOL_NORMAL; x < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; x++)
3940 {
3941 if (GetMiscValue() & int32(1 << x))
3942 {
3943 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_RESISTANCE_START + x), TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
3944 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER || target->IsPet())
3945 target->ApplyResistanceBuffModsMod(SpellSchools(x), GetAmount() > 0, (float)GetAmount(), apply);
3946 }
3947 }
3948}

4001void AuraEffect::HandleModTargetResistance(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4002{
4003 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4004 return;
4005
4006 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4007
4008 // applied to damage as HandleNoImmediateEffect in Unit::CalcAbsorbResist and Unit::CalcArmorReducedDamage
4009
4010 // show armor penetration
4011 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER && (GetMiscValue() & SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL))
4012 target->ApplyModInt32Value(PLAYER_FIELD_MOD_TARGET_PHYSICAL_RESISTANCE, GetAmount(), apply);
4013
4014 // show as spell penetration only full spell penetration bonuses (all resistances except armor and holy
4015 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER && (GetMiscValue() & SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_SPELL) == SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_SPELL)
4016 target->ApplyModInt32Value(PLAYER_FIELD_MOD_TARGET_RESISTANCE, GetAmount(), apply);
4017}

4019/********************************/
4020/*** STAT ***/
4021/********************************/
4022
4023void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModStat(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4024{
4025 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4026 return;
4027
4028 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4029
4030 if (GetMiscValue() < -2 || GetMiscValue() > 4)
4031 {
4032 LOG_ERROR("spells.aura.effect", "WARNING: Spell {} effect {} has an unsupported misc value ({}) for SPELL_AURA_MOD_STAT ", GetId(), GetEffIndex(), GetMiscValue());
4033 return;
4034 }
4035
4036 for (int32 i = STAT_STRENGTH; i < MAX_STATS; i++)
4037 {
4038 // -1 or -2 is all stats (misc < -2 checked in function beginning)
4039 if (GetMiscValue() < 0 || GetMiscValue() == i)
4040 {
4041 //target->ApplyStatMod(Stats(i), m_amount, apply);
4042 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_STAT_START + i), TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4043 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER || target->IsPet())
4044 target->ApplyStatBuffMod(Stats(i), (float)GetAmount(), apply);
4045 }
4046 }
4047}

4049void AuraEffect::HandleModPercentStat(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4050{
4051 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4052 return;
4053
4054 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4055
4056 if (GetMiscValue() < -1 || GetMiscValue() > 4)
4057 {
4058 LOG_ERROR("spells.aura.effect", "WARNING: Misc Value for SPELL_AURA_MOD_PERCENT_STAT not valid");
4059 return;
4060 }
4061
4062 // only players have base stats
4063 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
4064 return;
4065
4066 for (int32 i = STAT_STRENGTH; i < MAX_STATS; ++i)
4067 {
4068 if (GetMiscValue() == i || GetMiscValue() == -1)
4069 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_STAT_START + i), BASE_PCT, float(m_amount), apply);
4070 }
4071}

4146
4147void AuraEffect::HandleModTotalPercentStat(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4148{
4149 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4150 return;
4151
4152 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4153
4154 if (GetMiscValue() < -1 || GetMiscValue() > 4)
4155 {
4156 LOG_ERROR("spells.aura.effect", "WARNING: Misc Value for SPELL_AURA_MOD_PERCENT_STAT not valid");
4157 return;
4158 }
4159
4160 // save current health state
4161 float healthPct = target->GetHealthPct();
4162 bool alive = target->IsAlive();
4163 float value = GetAmount();
4164
4165 if (GetId() == 67480) // xinef: hack fix for blessing of sanctuary stats stack with blessing of kings...
4166 {
4167 if (value) // not turned off
4168 value = 10.0f;
4169 for (int32 i = STAT_STRENGTH; i < MAX_STATS; i++)
4170 {
4171 if (i == STAT_STRENGTH || i == STAT_STAMINA)
4172 {
4173 if (apply && (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER || target->IsPet()))
4174 target->ApplyStatPercentBuffMod(Stats(i), value, apply);
4175
4176 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_STAT_START + i), TOTAL_PCT, value, apply);
4177
4178 if (!apply && (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER || target->IsPet()))
4179 target->ApplyStatPercentBuffMod(Stats(i), value, apply);
4180 }
4181 }
4182 return;
4183 }
4184
4185 for (int32 i = STAT_STRENGTH; i < MAX_STATS; i++)
4186 {
4187 if (GetMiscValue() == i || GetMiscValue() == -1)
4188 {
4189 if (apply && (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER || target->IsPet()))
4190 target->ApplyStatPercentBuffMod(Stats(i), value, apply);
4191
4192 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_STAT_START + i), TOTAL_PCT, value, apply);
4193
4194 if (!apply && (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER || target->IsPet()))
4195 target->ApplyStatPercentBuffMod(Stats(i), value, apply);
4196 }
4197 }
4198
4199 // recalculate current HP/MP after applying aura modifications (only for spells with SPELL_ATTR0_UNK4 0x00000010 flag)
4200 if (GetMiscValue() == STAT_STAMINA && m_spellInfo->HasAttribute(SPELL_ATTR0_IS_ABILITY))
4201 target->SetHealth(std::max<uint32>(uint32(healthPct * target->GetMaxHealth() * 0.01f), (alive ? 1 : 0)));
4202}
4203
4204void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModResistenceOfStatPercent(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool /*apply*/) const
4205{
4206 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4207 return;
4208
4209 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4210
4211 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
4212 return;
4213
4214 if (GetMiscValue() != SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL)
4215 {
4216 // support required adding replace UpdateArmor by loop by UpdateResistence at intellect update
4217 // and include in UpdateResistence same code as in UpdateArmor for aura mod apply.
4218 LOG_ERROR("spells.aura.effect", "Aura SPELL_AURA_MOD_RESISTANCE_OF_STAT_PERCENT(182) does not work for non-armor type resistances!");
4219 return;
4220 }
4221
4222 // Recalculate Armor
4223 target->UpdateArmor();
4224}

4279
4280void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModIncreaseHealth(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4281{
4282 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4283 return;
4284
4285 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4286
4287 if (apply)
4288 {
4289 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_HEALTH, TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4290 target->ModifyHealth(GetAmount());
4291 }
4292 else
4293 {
4294 if (int32(target->GetHealth()) > GetAmount())
4295 target->ModifyHealth(-GetAmount());
4296 else
4297 target->SetHealth(1);
4298 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_HEALTH, TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4299 }
4300}
4301
4302void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModIncreaseMaxHealth(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4303{
4304 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4305 return;
4306
4307 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4308
4309 uint32 oldhealth = target->GetHealth();
4310 double healthPercentage = (double)oldhealth / (double)target->GetMaxHealth();
4311
4312 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_HEALTH, TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4313
4314 // refresh percentage
4315 if (oldhealth > 0)
4316 {
4317 uint32 newhealth = uint32(std::ceil((double)target->GetMaxHealth() * healthPercentage));
4318 if (newhealth == 0)
4319 newhealth = 1;
4320
4321 target->SetHealth(newhealth);
4322 }
4323}
4324
4325void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModIncreaseEnergy(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4326{
4327 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4328 return;
4329
4330 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4331
4332 Powers PowerType = Powers(GetMiscValue());
4333 // do not check power type, we can always modify the maximum
4334 // as the client will not see any difference
4335 // also, placing conditions that may change during the aura duration
4336 // inside effect handlers is not a good idea
4337 //if (int32(PowerType) != GetMiscValue())
4338 // return;
4339
4340 UnitMods unitMod = UnitMods(static_cast<uint16>(UNIT_MOD_POWER_START) + PowerType);
4341
4342 target->HandleStatModifier(unitMod, TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4343}
4344
4345void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModIncreaseEnergyPercent(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4346{
4347 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4348 return;
4349
4350 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4351
4352 Powers PowerType = Powers(GetMiscValue());
4353 // do not check power type, we can always modify the maximum
4354 // as the client will not see any difference
4355 // also, placing conditions that may change during the aura duration
4356 // inside effect handlers is not a good idea
4357 //if (int32(PowerType) != GetMiscValue())
4358 // return;
4359
4360 UnitMods unitMod = UnitMods(static_cast<uint16>(UNIT_MOD_POWER_START) + PowerType);
4361 float amount = float(GetAmount());
4362
4363 if (apply)
4364 {
4365 target->HandleStatModifier(unitMod, TOTAL_PCT, amount, apply);
4366 target->ModifyPowerPct(PowerType, amount, apply);
4367 }
4368 else
4369 {
4370 target->ModifyPowerPct(PowerType, amount, apply);
4371 target->HandleStatModifier(unitMod, TOTAL_PCT, amount, apply);
4372 }
4373}
4374
4375void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModIncreaseHealthPercent(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4376{
4377 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4378 return;
4379
4380 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4381
4382 // Unit will keep hp% after MaxHealth being modified if unit is alive.
4383 float percent = target->GetHealthPct();
4384 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_HEALTH, TOTAL_PCT, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4385
4386 // Xinef: pct was rounded down and could "kill" creature by setting its health to 0 making npc zombie
4387 if (target->IsAlive())
4388 if (uint32 healthAmount = CalculatePct(target->GetMaxHealth(), percent))
4389 target->SetHealth(healthAmount);
4390}

4395 return;

4400}

4453void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModWeaponCritPercent(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4454{
4455 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4456 return;
4457
4458 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4459
4460 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
4461 return;
4462
4463 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_ATTACK; ++i)
4464 if (Item* pItem = target->ToPlayer()->GetWeaponForAttack(WeaponAttackType(i), true))
4465 target->ToPlayer()->_ApplyWeaponDependentAuraCritMod(pItem, WeaponAttackType(i), this, apply);
4466
4467 // mods must be applied base at equipped weapon class and subclass comparison
4468 // with spell->EquippedItemClass and EquippedItemSubClassMask and EquippedItemInventoryTypeMask
4469 // GetMiscValue() comparison with item generated damage types
4470
4471 if (GetSpellInfo()->EquippedItemClass == -1)
4472 {
4473 target->ToPlayer()->HandleBaseModValue(CRIT_PERCENTAGE, FLAT_MOD, float (GetAmount()), apply);
4474 target->ToPlayer()->HandleBaseModValue(OFFHAND_CRIT_PERCENTAGE, FLAT_MOD, float (GetAmount()), apply);
4475 target->ToPlayer()->HandleBaseModValue(RANGED_CRIT_PERCENTAGE, FLAT_MOD, float (GetAmount()), apply);
4476 }
4477 else
4478 {
4479 // done in Player::_ApplyWeaponDependentAuraMods
4480 }
4481}

4483void AuraEffect::HandleModHitChance(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4484{
4485 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4486 return;

4489
4490 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
4491 {
4492 target->ToPlayer()->UpdateMeleeHitChances();
4493 target->ToPlayer()->UpdateRangedHitChances();
4494 }
4495 else
4496 {
4497 target->m_modMeleeHitChance += (apply) ? GetAmount() : (-GetAmount());
4498 target->m_modRangedHitChance += (apply) ? GetAmount() : (-GetAmount());
4499 }
4500}

4770/********************************/
4771/*** DAMAGE BONUS ***/
4772/********************************/
4773void AuraEffect::HandleModDamageDone(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4774{
4775 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4776 return;
4777
4778 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4779
4780 // apply item specific bonuses for already equipped weapon
4781 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
4782 {
4783 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_ATTACK; ++i)
4784 if (Item* pItem = target->ToPlayer()->GetWeaponForAttack(WeaponAttackType(i), true))
4785 target->ToPlayer()->_ApplyWeaponDependentAuraDamageMod(pItem, WeaponAttackType(i), this, apply);
4786 }
4787
4788 // GetMiscValue() is bitmask of spell schools
4789 // 1 (0-bit) - normal school damage (SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL)
4790 // 126 - full bitmask all magic damages (SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_MAGIC) including wands
4791 // 127 - full bitmask any damages
4792 //
4793 // mods must be applied base at equipped weapon class and subclass comparison
4794 // with spell->EquippedItemClass and EquippedItemSubClassMask and EquippedItemInventoryTypeMask
4795 // GetMiscValue() comparison with item generated damage types
4796
4797 if ((GetMiscValue() & SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL) != 0 && sScriptMgr->CanModAuraEffectDamageDone(this, target, aurApp, mode, apply))
4798 {
4799 // apply generic physical damage bonuses including wand case
4800 if (GetSpellInfo()->EquippedItemClass == -1 || target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
4801 {
4802 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_DAMAGE_MAINHAND, TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4803 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_DAMAGE_OFFHAND, TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4804 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_DAMAGE_RANGED, TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4805
4806 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
4807 {
4808 if (GetAmount() > 0)
4809 target->ApplyModInt32Value(PLAYER_FIELD_MOD_DAMAGE_DONE_POS, GetAmount(), apply);
4810 else
4811 target->ApplyModInt32Value(PLAYER_FIELD_MOD_DAMAGE_DONE_NEG, GetAmount(), apply);
4812 }
4813 }
4814 else
4815 {
4816 // done in Player::_ApplyWeaponDependentAuraMods
4817 }
4818 }
4819
4820 // Skip non magic case for Speedup
4821 if ((GetMiscValue() & SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_MAGIC) == 0)
4822 return;
4823
4824 if (GetSpellInfo()->EquippedItemClass != -1 || GetSpellInfo()->EquippedItemInventoryTypeMask != 0)
4825 {
4826 // wand magic case (skip generic to all item spell bonuses)
4827 // done in Player::_ApplyWeaponDependentAuraMods
4828
4829 // Skip item specific requirements for not wand magic damage
4830 return;
4831 }
4832
4833 // Magic damage modifiers implemented in Unit::SpellDamageBonus
4834 // This information for client side use only
4835 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
4836 {
4837 if (GetAmount() > 0)
4838 {
4839 for (uint32 i = SPELL_SCHOOL_HOLY; i < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; i++)
4840 {
4841 if ((GetMiscValue() & (1 << i)) != 0)
4842 target->ApplyModInt32Value(PLAYER_FIELD_MOD_DAMAGE_DONE_POS + i, GetAmount(), apply);
4843 }
4844 }
4845 else
4846 {
4847 for (uint32 i = SPELL_SCHOOL_HOLY; i < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; i++)
4848 {
4849 if ((GetMiscValue() & (1 << i)) != 0)
4850 target->ApplyModInt32Value(PLAYER_FIELD_MOD_DAMAGE_DONE_NEG + i, GetAmount(), apply);
4851 }
4852 }
4853 if (Guardian* pet = target->ToPlayer()->GetGuardianPet())
4854 pet->UpdateAttackPowerAndDamage();
4855 }
4856}
4857
4858void AuraEffect::HandleModDamagePercentDone(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4859{
4860 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4861 return;
4862
4863 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4864 if (!target)
4865 return;
4866
4867 if (!sScriptMgr->CanModAuraEffectModDamagePercentDone(this, target, aurApp, mode, apply))
4868 return;
4869
4870 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
4871 {
4872 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_ATTACK; ++i)
4873 if (Item* item = target->ToPlayer()->GetWeaponForAttack(WeaponAttackType(i), false))
4874 target->ToPlayer()->_ApplyWeaponDependentAuraDamageMod(item, WeaponAttackType(i), this, apply);
4875 }
4876
4877 if ((GetMiscValue() & SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL) && (GetSpellInfo()->EquippedItemClass == -1 || target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER))
4878 {
4879 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_DAMAGE_MAINHAND, TOTAL_PCT, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4880 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_DAMAGE_OFFHAND, TOTAL_PCT, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4881 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_DAMAGE_RANGED, TOTAL_PCT, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4882
4883 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
4884 target->ToPlayer()->ApplyPercentModFloatValue(PLAYER_FIELD_MOD_DAMAGE_DONE_PCT, float (GetAmount()), apply);
4885 }
4886 else
4887 {
4888 // done in Player::_ApplyWeaponDependentAuraMods for SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL && EquippedItemClass != -1 and also for wand case
4889 }
4890}
4891
4892void AuraEffect::HandleModOffhandDamagePercent(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4893{
4894 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4895 return;
4896
4897 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4898
4899 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_DAMAGE_OFFHAND, TOTAL_PCT, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4900}
4901
4902void AuraEffect::HandleShieldBlockValue(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4903{
4904 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4905 return;
4906
4907 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4908
4909 BaseModType modType = FLAT_MOD;
4910 if (GetAuraType() == SPELL_AURA_MOD_SHIELD_BLOCKVALUE_PCT)
4911 modType = PCT_MOD;
4912
4913 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
4914 target->ToPlayer()->HandleBaseModValue(SHIELD_BLOCK_VALUE, modType, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4915}

4917/********************************/
4918/*** POWER COST ***/
4919/********************************/
4920
4921void AuraEffect::HandleModPowerCostPCT(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4922{
4923 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK))
4924 return;
4925
4926 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4927
4928 float amount = CalculatePct(1.0f, GetAmount());
4929 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; ++i)
4930 if (GetMiscValue() & (1 << i))
4931 target->ApplyModSignedFloatValue(UNIT_FIELD_POWER_COST_MULTIPLIER + i, amount, apply);
4932}
4933
4934void AuraEffect::HandleModPowerCost(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4935{
4936 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK))
4937 return;
4938
4939 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4940
4941 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; ++i)
4942 if (GetMiscValue() & (1 << i))
4943 target->ApplyModInt32Value(UNIT_FIELD_POWER_COST_MODIFIER + i, GetAmount(), apply);
4944}
4945
4946void AuraEffect::HandleArenaPreparation(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4947{
4948 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
4949 return;
4950
4951 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4952
4953 if (apply)
4954 target->SetUnitFlag(UNIT_FLAG_PREPARATION);
4955 else
4956 {
4957 // do not remove unit flag if there are more than this auraEffect of that kind on unit on unit
4958 if (target->HasAuraType(GetAuraType()))
4959 return;
4960 target->RemoveUnitFlag(UNIT_FLAG_PREPARATION);
4961 }
4962}
4963
4964void AuraEffect::HandleNoReagentUseAura(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool /*apply*/) const
4965{
4966 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
4967 return;
4968
4969 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4970
4971 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
4972 return;
4973
4974 flag96 mask;
4975 Unit::AuraEffectList const& noReagent = target->GetAuraEffectsByType(SPELL_AURA_NO_REAGENT_USE);
4976 for (Unit::AuraEffectList::const_iterator i = noReagent.begin(); i != noReagent.end(); ++i)
4977 mask |= (*i)->m_spellInfo->Effects[(*i)->m_effIndex].SpellClassMask;
4978
4979 target->SetUInt32Value(PLAYER_NO_REAGENT_COST_1, mask[0]);
4980 target->SetUInt32Value(PLAYER_NO_REAGENT_COST_1 + 1, mask[1]);
4981 target->SetUInt32Value(PLAYER_NO_REAGENT_COST_1 + 2, mask[2]);
4982}
4983
4984void AuraEffect::HandleAuraRetainComboPoints(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4985{
4986 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
4987 return;
4988
4989 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4990
4991 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
4992 return;
4993
4994 // combo points was added in SPELL_EFFECT_ADD_COMBO_POINTS handler
4995 // remove only if aura expire by time (in case combo points amount change aura removed without combo points lost)
4996 if (!(apply) && GetBase()->GetDuration() == 0)
4997 target->AddComboPoints(-GetAmount());
4998}

5032 case 1515: // Tame beast

5052 Aura* pet_aura = pet->GetAura(58914, GetCasterGUID());

5061 }
5062 }
5063 break;
5064 }
5065 case 37096: // Blood Elf Illusion

5070 {

5072 caster->CastSpell(target, 37095, true, nullptr, this); // Blood Elf Disguise
5073 break;
5074 case GENDER_MALE:

5452
5453void AuraEffect::HandleChannelDeathItem(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5454{
5455 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5456 return;
5457
5458 if (apply || aurApp->GetRemoveMode() != AURA_REMOVE_BY_DEATH)
5459 return;
5460
5461 Unit* caster = GetCaster();
5462
5463 if (!caster || caster->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
5464 return;
5465
5466 Player* plCaster = caster->ToPlayer();
5467
5468 // Item amount
5469 if (GetAmount() <= 0)
5470 return;
5471
5472 if (GetSpellInfo()->Effects[m_effIndex].ItemType == 0)
5473 return;
5474
5475 //Adding items
5476 uint32 noSpaceForCount = 0;
5477 uint32 count = m_amount;
5478
5479 ItemPosCountVec dest;
5480 InventoryResult msg = plCaster->CanStoreNewItem(NULL_BAG, NULL_SLOT, dest, GetSpellInfo()->Effects[m_effIndex].ItemType, count, &noSpaceForCount);
5481 if (msg != EQUIP_ERR_OK)
5482 {
5483 count -= noSpaceForCount;
5484 plCaster->SendEquipError(msg, nullptr, nullptr, GetSpellInfo()->Effects[m_effIndex].ItemType);
5485 if (count == 0)
5486 return;
5487 }
5488
5489 Item* newitem = plCaster->StoreNewItem(dest, GetSpellInfo()->Effects[m_effIndex].ItemType, true);
5490 if (!newitem)
5491 {
5492 plCaster->SendEquipError(EQUIP_ERR_ITEM_NOT_FOUND, nullptr, nullptr);
5493 return;
5494 }
5495 plCaster->SendNewItem(newitem, count, true, true);
5496}
5497
5498void AuraEffect::HandleBindSight(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5499{
5500 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5501 return;
5502
5503 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5504
5505 Unit* caster = GetCaster();
5506
5507 if (!caster || caster->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
5508 return;
5509
5510 caster->ToPlayer()->SetViewpoint(target, apply);
5511}

5517 return;
5518 }

5522 {

5538
5539void AuraEffect::HandleForceReaction(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5540{
5541 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK))
5542 return;
5543
5544 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5545
5546 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
5547 return;
5548
5549 Player* player = target->ToPlayer();
5550
5551 uint32 faction_id = GetMiscValue();
5552 ReputationRank faction_rank = ReputationRank(m_amount);
5553
5554 player->GetReputationMgr().ApplyForceReaction(faction_id, faction_rank, apply);
5555 player->GetReputationMgr().SendForceReactions();
5556
5557 // stop fighting if at apply forced rank friendly or at remove real rank friendly
5558 if ((apply && faction_rank >= REP_FRIENDLY) || (!apply && player->GetReputationRank(faction_id) >= REP_FRIENDLY))
5559 player->StopAttackFaction(faction_id);
5560}

5562void AuraEffect::HandleAuraEmpathy(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5563{
5564 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5565 return;
5566
5567 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5568
5569 if (!apply)
5570 {
5571 // do not remove unit flag if there are more than this auraEffect of that kind on unit on unit
5572 if (target->HasAuraType(GetAuraType()))
5573 return;
5574 }
5575
5576 if (target->GetCreatureType() == CREATURE_TYPE_BEAST)
5577 target->ApplyModUInt32Value(UNIT_DYNAMIC_FLAGS, UNIT_DYNFLAG_SPECIALINFO, apply);
5578}

5592 }
5593 else

5595 target->RestoreFaction();
5596 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
5597 target->SetUnitFlag(UNIT_FLAG_PLAYER_CONTROLLED);
5598 }

5618
5619void AuraEffect::HandleAuraConvertRune(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5620{
5621 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5622 return;
5623
5624 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5625
5626 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
5627 return;
5628
5629 Player* player = target->ToPlayer();
5630
5631 if (player->getClass() != CLASS_DEATH_KNIGHT)
5632 return;
5633
5634 uint32 runes = m_amount;
5635 // convert number of runes specified in aura amount of rune type in miscvalue to runetype in miscvalueb
5636 if (apply)
5637 {
5638 for (uint32 i = 0; i < MAX_RUNES && runes; ++i)
5639 {
5640 if (GetMiscValue() != player->GetCurrentRune(i))
5641 continue;
5642 if (!player->GetRuneCooldown(i))
5643 {
5644 player->AddRuneByAuraEffect(i, RuneType(GetMiscValueB()), this);
5645 --runes;
5646 }
5647 }
5648 }
5649 else
5650 player->RemoveRunesByAuraEffect(this);
5651}
5652
5653void AuraEffect::HandleAuraLinked(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5654{
5655 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5656
5657 uint32 triggeredSpellId = sSpellMgr->GetSpellIdForDifficulty(m_spellInfo->Effects[m_effIndex].TriggerSpell, target);
5658 SpellInfo const* triggeredSpellInfo = sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(triggeredSpellId);
5659 if (!triggeredSpellInfo)
5660 return;
5661
5662 if (mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL)
5663 {
5664 if (apply)
5665 {
5666 Unit* caster = triggeredSpellInfo->NeedsToBeTriggeredByCaster(m_spellInfo, GetEffIndex()) ? GetCaster() : target;
5667
5668 if (!caster)
5669 return;
5670 // If amount avalible cast with basepoints (Crypt Fever for example)
5671 if (GetAmount())
5672 caster->CastCustomSpell(target, triggeredSpellId, &m_amount, nullptr, nullptr, true, nullptr, this);
5673 else
5674 caster->CastSpell(target, triggeredSpellId, true, nullptr, this);
5675 }
5676 else
5677 {
5678 ObjectGuid casterGUID = triggeredSpellInfo->NeedsToBeTriggeredByCaster(m_spellInfo, GetEffIndex()) ? GetCasterGUID() : target->GetGUID();
5679 target->RemoveAura(triggeredSpellId, casterGUID, 0, aurApp->GetRemoveMode());
5680 }
5681 }
5682 else if (mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAPPLY && apply)
5683 {
5684 ObjectGuid casterGUID = triggeredSpellInfo->NeedsToBeTriggeredByCaster(m_spellInfo, GetEffIndex()) ? GetCasterGUID() : target->GetGUID();
5685 // change the stack amount to be equal to stack amount of our aura
5686 if (Aura* triggeredAura = target->GetAura(triggeredSpellId, casterGUID))
5687 triggeredAura->ModStackAmount(GetBase()->GetStackAmount() - triggeredAura->GetStackAmount());
5688 }
5689}
5690

5692{
5693 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5694 return;
5695
5696 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5697
5698 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER || !target->IsInWorld())
5699 return;
5700
5701 if (apply)
5702 target->ToPlayer()->GetSession()->SendStablePet(target->GetGUID());
5703
5704 // client auto close stable dialog at !apply aura
5705}
5706
5707void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModFakeInebriation(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5708{
5709 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK))
5710 return;
5711
5712 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5713
5714 if (apply)
5715 {
5716 target->m_invisibilityDetect.AddFlag(INVISIBILITY_DRUNK);
5717 target->m_invisibilityDetect.AddValue(INVISIBILITY_DRUNK, GetAmount());
5718
5719 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
5720 {
5721 int32 oldval = target->ToPlayer()->GetInt32Value(PLAYER_FAKE_INEBRIATION);
5722 target->ToPlayer()->SetInt32Value(PLAYER_FAKE_INEBRIATION, oldval + GetAmount());
5723 }
5724 }
5725 else
5726 {
5727 bool removeDetect = !target->HasAuraType(SPELL_AURA_MOD_FAKE_INEBRIATE);
5728
5729 target->m_invisibilityDetect.AddValue(INVISIBILITY_DRUNK, -GetAmount());
5730
5731 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
5732 {
5733 int32 oldval = target->ToPlayer()->GetInt32Value(PLAYER_FAKE_INEBRIATION);
5734 target->ToPlayer()->SetInt32Value(PLAYER_FAKE_INEBRIATION, oldval - GetAmount());
5735
5736 if (removeDetect)
5737 removeDetect = !target->ToPlayer()->GetDrunkValue();
5738 }
5739
5740 if (removeDetect)
5741 target->m_invisibilityDetect.DelFlag(INVISIBILITY_DRUNK);
5742 }
5743
5744 // call functions which may have additional effects after chainging state of unit
5745 target->UpdateObjectVisibility(false);
5746}
5747
5748void AuraEffect::HandleAuraOverrideSpells(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5749{
5750 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5751 return;
5752
5753 Player* target = aurApp->GetTarget()->ToPlayer();
5754
5755 if (!target || !target->IsInWorld())
5756 return;
5757
5758 uint32 overrideId = uint32(GetMiscValue());
5759
5760 if (apply)
5761 {
5762 target->SetUInt16Value(PLAYER_FIELD_BYTES2, PLAYER_BYTES_2_OVERRIDE_SPELLS_UINT16_OFFSET, overrideId);
5763 if (OverrideSpellDataEntry const* overrideSpells = sOverrideSpellDataStore.LookupEntry(overrideId))
5764 for (uint8 i = 0; i < MAX_OVERRIDE_SPELL; ++i)
5765 if (uint32 spellId = overrideSpells->spellId[i])
5766 target->_addSpell(spellId, SPEC_MASK_ALL, true);
5767 }
5768 else
5769 {
5770 target->SetUInt16Value(PLAYER_FIELD_BYTES2, PLAYER_BYTES_2_OVERRIDE_SPELLS_UINT16_OFFSET, 0);
5771 if (OverrideSpellDataEntry const* overrideSpells = sOverrideSpellDataStore.LookupEntry(overrideId))
5772 for (uint8 i = 0; i < MAX_OVERRIDE_SPELL; ++i)
5773 if (uint32 spellId = overrideSpells->spellId[i])
5774 target->removeSpell(spellId, SPEC_MASK_ALL, true);
5775 }
5776}
5777
5778void AuraEffect::HandleAuraSetVehicle(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5779{
5780 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5781 return;
5782
5783 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5784
5785 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER || !target->IsInWorld())
5786 return;
5787
5788 uint32 vehicleId = GetMiscValue();
5789
5790 if (apply)
5791 {
5792 if (!target->CreateVehicleKit(vehicleId, 0))
5793 return;
5794 }
5795 else if (target->GetVehicleKit())
5796 target->RemoveVehicleKit();
5797
5798 WorldPacket data(SMSG_PLAYER_VEHICLE_DATA, target->GetPackGUID().size() + 4);
5799 data << target->GetPackGUID();
5800 data << uint32(apply ? vehicleId : 0);
5801 target->SendMessageToSet(&data, true);
5802
5803 if (apply)
5804 {
5805 data.Initialize(SMSG_ON_CANCEL_EXPECTED_RIDE_VEHICLE_AURA, 0);
5806 target->ToPlayer()->GetSession()->SendPacket(&data);
5807 }
5808}

5810void AuraEffect::HandlePreventResurrection(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5811{
